sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as 前端
    participant SB as Spring Boot
    participant Flask as Flask AI
    participant FS as FaceService
    participant CC as ConfigClient
    
    Note over FE,CC: 人脸注册
    FE->>SB: POST /students/{id}/face
    SB->>Flask: POST /face/feature/extract
    Flask->>FS: extract_feature_from_base64
    FS->>FS: InsightFace 检测+提取特征
    FS-->>SB: feature_vector
    SB->>SB: 保存到 face_feature 表
    SB-->>FE: 注册成功
    
    Note over FE,CC: 实时识别
    Flask->>CC: get_face_features()
    Flask->>FS: recognize_frame(frame, cache)
    FS->>FS: 计算余弦相似度
    FS-->>Flask: 事件列表